

1 Install User Authentication

Laravel needs a **login/register system** first.

Run:

```bash
composer require laravel/breeze --dev
php artisan breeze:install blade
npm install
npm run dev
php artisan migrate
```

This creates:

```
/login
/register
/dashboard
```

Now **users can create accounts and login**.

