7 Controller for Showing Post

Example:

`HomeController.php`

```php
public function show($id)
{
    $post = Post::with('comments.user')->findOrFail($id);

    return view('user.post',compact('post'));
}
```

---

8 Add Route for Viewing Post

```
routes/web.php
```

```php
Route::get('/post/{id}',[HomeController::class,'show']);
```

